Message.En: The Poet Who Holds His Tongue

I intended to sing about the current state of
the Urteca Mountains to the citizens of Megado,
but it seems it's not in a state to be shared.
No one would want to hear a song about being
attacked by <LQVA> <LQEM> 
and losing one's belongings.
Message.Jp:
ウルテカ山岳の現状を、メガドの市民にも
唄って聞かせようと思ったのですが
聞かせられる状態ではありませんね
<LQVA>匹の<LQEM>に襲われ、あげく荷物を失った歌など
誰も聞きたくはないでしょうから
